Solution:

Instead of using jakarta.annotation-api library. I used javax.annotation-api external library and it solved my problem.

    &lt;dependency&gt;
    &lt;groupId&gt;javax.annotation&lt;/groupId&gt;
    &lt;artifactId&gt;javax.annotation-api&lt;/artifactId&gt;
    &lt;version&gt;1.3.2&lt;/version&gt;
&lt;/dependency&gt;

Explanation : Until Spring Boot 2.7.x were using javax.* but after Spring Boot 3.x Spring Boot that makes use of Jakarta EE 9 APIs (jakarta.*) instead of EE 8 (javax.*)

That means, when I upgrade my spring from 2.7 to 3.0, I have to replace javax with jakarta.

